World coastal lines LINESTRING object

Source: R/data.R
gisco_coastallines_20M_2016.Rd

A sf object including the coast lines as provided by GISCO (2016 version).

Format

A LINESTRING data frame (resolution: 1:20million, EPSG:4326) object with 8 variables:

EFTA_FLAG

Coast belonging to EFTA countries

OTHR_FLAG

Coast belonging to other countries

EU_FLAG

Coast belonging to EU countries

COAS_FLAG

Coast flag

CNTR_BN_ID

CNTR_BN_ID

CC_FLAG

Coast belonging to EU candidate countries

FID

FID

geometry

geometry field

Source

GISCO .geojson source
